title: Grateful Dead Live at Silver Stadium on 1987-07-02
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket-> Bertha, Walkin' Blues, Dire Wolf, My Brother Esau, When Push Comes To Shove, Tons Of Steel, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Brown Eyed Women, Cassidy, Deal

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Samson & Delilah, Looks Like Rain, He's Gone-> Jam-> Drums-> Space-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> All Along The Watchtower-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Black Muddy River

reviews.review_text: Just Exactly Perfect! This recording is beyond compare.  Balanced separation, just enough crowd, silky sweet, everybody's in there, and crystal clear.

the "phoenix" show! hey, my first show ;) in standard linear time, that is. thanks for the nice recording. i remember wandering by the the taper section for the first time ever, thinking, are we still on earth? peace, s.
